 public Imagick Imagick::similarityImage
 Imagickimage
 arrayoffset&null;
 floatsimilarity&null;
 floatthreshold0.0
 intmetric0


 Searches the current image for the given subimage and returns a new image
 in which the location of the best match is highlighted. The area of closest
 correspondence appears brightest in the returned similarity map.

&reftitle.returnvalues;

 Returns a new Imagick object containing the
 similarity map.
